explanation: [0-0] A girl stands on the pool deck of a swimming pool, wearing a yellow jersey and blue shorts, her hair is black. The girl's head turns to the right rear, her eyes looking at the camera. The girl's upper body leans slightly to the right, her right hand makes a fist and raises, her arm bends back forcefully. Her right foot steps on a yellow soccer ball. There are ten jerseys of different styles and colors on the pool deck in front of the girl. On the other side of the aisle stands a boy, wearing a black and white vertical striped short-sleeved shirt and white shorts, with both hands clenched and raised and bent. Behind the boy is a wall, the upper part of the wall is painted yellow, the lower part is decorated with different shapes of marble. Between the wall and the pool, there are two unopened umbrellas on the lawn.

[0-8] The girl and the boy face the camera to cheer up, the girl turns around and kicks the soccer ball, the camera follows the rolling of the soccer ball and keeps zooming in, finally the soccer ball stops at the yellow jersey with green and blue No. 10, the jersey is printed with the letters "NEYMHR JR". Then the camera zooms out, the girl holds the jersey in front of her with both hands and shakes it, then the picture turns, the girl wears the yellow jersey, smiles, opens her hands slightly shrugs, and jumps towards the pool. The girl jumps up and makes a gesture of putting her hands together on her cheeks and closing her eyes, imitating the "sleeping" action of the star Neymar.
